Changing owners to files/folders:
chown username filename : to change the owner for any file.
chgrp group name filename: to change the group of a file.
chown owner name : group name filename : to change the user and group at a time.
chown user:group * : to change user and group at a time for all files.
chown user:group file1 file2 file3 : to change the user and group for ,ultiple files at a time.
